The purpose of this project is to set up an Nginx load balancer server with Ansible inside Docker containers.

command to exceute :

1- Build services : docker-compose up -d
2- Execute ansible playbook inside the master container : docker-compose exec master ansible-playbook /etc/ansible/playbooks/playbook.yml
3- Run Curl command from the machine that you map it with the lb container : curl locaalhost or curl "lb_ip_address"(172.17.0.4)





